41,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:15:34.000Z","msg":"我認我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭廉航我永遠都9個字至1粒鐘先去check in<br />\n因為可以唔洗排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncheck in完再過埋海關屙埋個屎差唔多就召集"},{"pid":"dd77067070dd3345632d480236ae392bbad47fe6","tid":19332,"uid":18179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:26:16.000Z","msg":"我一般早個半鐘到<br />\ncheck-in行李，過禁區都要起碼半粒鐘<br />\n如果要去啲無雷公咁遠嘅boarding gate又要預返十幾廿分鐘<br />\n加埋搭車 / 揸車去機場要預埋交通問題<br />\n咁就差唔多啦 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa937914b5de09af5bd4c6b3c46b0153fb6ac204","tid":19332,"uid":50893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老實講 早checkin 係for 人將你啲行李上機 <br />\n唔係就你  如果你遲左<br />\n分分鍾去到目的地 <br />\n仲要等下一班機先有行李拎 <br />\n飛機唔會為左果少少行李delay <br />\n利申：做緊機場 2個鍾係啱啱好</blockquote><br />\n坐 ID90 都未遇過啲咁嘅嘢喎，行李 delay 有幾可發生？行李 delay 似係地勤失誤多過 check-in 太遲囉</blockquote><br />\n基本上每班機都會有幾件rush係 上一班留低 數量唔多 但有，咁果啲係咪要等呀 咪係啲人遲到 件野去到果時架機要走就會cut <br />\n同埋你checkin完唔係直到飛機好冇 中間啲行程老鏈咁多 地勤唔洗時間做呀 又唔係正係做你一件，一班機講緊3 ，4百喎 唔好咩都話人失誤啦香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己行李自己有責任 同時請你體諒下其他人做野既辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a268f09e639b0e0df1b983149593c2582b1c3e","tid":19332,"uid":37717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"順便問埋各位巴打，長假期朝早十一點機，諗住八點係屋企飛的去機鐵站，會唔會太抆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0242634db8563ad0bb5d49682c5cf6c4f39a2806","tid":19332,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:32:12.000Z","msg":"個post似曾相識咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7389cc78d3c81b355616b4806bb09b5356be8100","tid":19332,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:33:02.000Z","msg":"早一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdb181ad7bd84b932a9a7a6a4a7bb28fcb98568","tid":19332,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你試過遲去check in 航空公司同你講班機爆哂要搭下班去<br />\n仲要同friend 去但得自己一條友搭下班機果下你就唔會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但班機爆哂個責任唔起你度喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無錢賠 ?"},{"pid":"8c4315330528f27def52a59fa60d9c90d12e78ba","tid":19332,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:35:33.000Z","msg":"早2個鐘到<br />\n搵位check in<br />\n排隊<br />\n過security check<br />\n食野/行街/打卡<br />\n其實2個鐘岩岩好<br />\n<br />\n如果想睇多D個機場就3個鐘"},{"pid":"ae52f39f26aa9a7d3252d35a7df813049833ac5f","tid":19332,"uid":7985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"差唔多每次都會提早個幾鐘至兩個鐘去check in先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前喺加拿大返香港個時超賣 有3個人無機位 搞到空姐要喺上機櫃位度問有無人肯換聽日班機 送返d vouchers咁 見到咁樣真係以後都唔敢遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a881c04888823c2714dcb71677b27769f725d6e","tid":19332,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOn 9有lounge 入去食個飯沖個涼都去左啦。唔係要張鑽石咭黎做乜"},{"pid":"84f0a3fdde25a1e83ba111fd9e37e6ba68fd07df","tid":19332,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"其實只係香港處理成個流程比較快，外國d機場鬼撚咁慢又多人，又唔熟路，2個鐘真係岩岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0e8f19e83fbd42d8a155941bb38e639d7e7c06","tid":19332,"uid":28051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,